From 2ad28cd7b121e327e8f86444090e5a7afd357d44 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>
Date: Thu, 23 Apr 2026 17:55:41 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] ask: netfilter qosmark/qosconnmark + comcerto_fp module

New netfilter matches + targets: xt_qosmark, xt_qosconnmark, and the
comcerto_fp_netfilter module that glues the fast path to netfilter's
packet-pipeline hooks. Declares CONFIG_NETFILTER_XT_QOSMARK and
CONFIG_NETFILTER_XT_QOSCONNMARK (both depend on CPE_FAST_PATH from 010).

Also the matching UAPI headers (xt_qosmark.h, xt_QOSMARK.h,
xt_qosconnmark.h, xt_QOSCONNMARK.h).

Signed-off-by: Tomaz Zaman <tomaz@mono.si>
